title: Did someone say Dream Home? Home in Tacoma. 4 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: You will instantly fall in love w/this stunning craftsman on an oversized corner lot.

new interior paint, kitchen & bathroom flooring, refinished cabinets & beautiful butcher block countertop pair w/the classic charm of original fir floors, detailed wood work & endless built-ins creating an elegant and functional showstopper.
Snuggle up in front of the fireplace on chilly evenings or entertain around the outdoor firepit in your fully-fenced backyard.
This home features 4 lg beds, 2 full baths, eating nook, mudroom & spacious formal living & dining areas.
The huge unfinished daylight basement w/separate entrance & detached garage/shop hold incredible potential for sweat equity.
